List of !OpenBiomind commands:

   * EnhanceDataset
   * DatasetTransformer
   * MetaTask
   * UtilityComputer
   * ClusteringTransformer
   * [http://code.google.com/p/openbiomind/wiki/Clusterize Clusterize]
   * ViewClusters
   * GraphFeatures
   * CompletePipeline

Note: in all commands above, the _openbiomind.jar_ executable, as well as the _pipeline.properites_ file and the _datafiles_ directory present at the extras package, are assumed to be in the classpath. Indeed often openbiomind.jar is evoked explicitly in the command line for sake of emphasis.
